      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable option for those who prioritize utility over aesthetics. The engine and transmission are in good working order, though you may notice some minor cosmetic wear on the exterior and some staining on the interior upholstery. It has been regularly maintained, but expect some upcoming minor repairs like brake pad replacement or addressing a small suspension creak. Overall, it's a solid, honest car that gets the job done without the premium price tag of a newer model.",
