    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously cared-for vehicle that strikes the perfect balance between luxury and everyday utility. This car features a deep, lustrous exterior finish that has been regularly waxed, though it shows the honest, minor character marks one would expect from a well-loved daily driver. Inside, you\u2019ll find a smoke-free cabin with supple leather seating that remains supportive and clean, complemented by a fully functional infotainment suite and dual-zone climate control. Mechanically, this car is a testament to proactive maintenance; it shifts smoothly through all gears, the engine purrs with consistent power, and the brakes provide firm, confident stopping power. Recent service includes a fresh oil change and a multi-point inspection, ensuring the new owner can drive away with peace of mind. Complete with a set of premium tires with ample tread remaining, this vehicle is ready for its next chapter. Serious buyers are invited to experience its refined road manners in person.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle represents a premier opportunity for the discerning driver. Offering a refined balance of performance and reliability, it has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure it meets our exacting standards for mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. An exceptional value for those seeking quality and longevity without compromise.",
      "price": 34900.0,
